{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016B7GEyXBphvmH3bw1CkA4w","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective written to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md`.\n\nKey findings:\n\n- **Session 50** was the 34th consecutive no-op session fixing the same Ralph stale-state corruption (stories 16-5 through 16-8 reverted to `review`).\n- **Total sprint cost: $714.12** across 5,250 API calls for 74 completed stories.\n- **~$235 (33%) is identifiable waste** from 34 repair loops, 34 retrospectives, and phantom story \"1-1-foo\" processing.\n- **Effective cost per real story: $9.65** (excluding waste).\n- **Verification phase consumed 54.2%** of total cost ($387).\n- **The P0 action item remains: kill Ralph.** The sprint has been complete since session 16. Every session after that has been pure token burn."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a3aa882605817c3fe (use SendMessage with to: 'a3aa882605817c3fe' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 40081\ntool_uses: 10\nduration_ms: 101081</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"87438d0a-1ce2-4205-b568-c91adcc95460","uuid":"b9353c26-a3e8-4557-8259-288cb3ae0c3d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:44:52.804Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Run /retrospective for the current sprint session.\n\nSprint status: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml\nSession issues log: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md\nCost report: Run `codeharness stats --json` to get token consumption data.\n\nCRITICAL: Read the session issues log FIRST. This file contains real problems, workarounds, bugs, and observations reported by every subagent that ran this session. These are the raw materials for your retrospective — do not ignore them.\n\nCRITICAL: Run `codeharness stats --save` to generate the cost report. Read `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md` and include cost analysis in the retrospective.\n\nCRITICAL: The session issues log contains `## Token Report` sections from each subagent. Aggregate these to understand WHERE tokens were spent inside subagents (not just the parent). Look for:\n- Which subagent phases had the most tool calls?\n- Which subagents read the same files repeatedly?\n- Which Bash commands produced the largest outputs?\n- What redundant operations were reported?\nInclude this subagent-level breakdown in the cost analysis section.\n\nThis is session 50, a no-op session that only fixed state corruption (34th time). All 74 stories are done across 17 epics. Ralph keeps reverting stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 to `review` due to stale in-memory state.\n\nProduce a retrospective that covers:\n1. **Session summary** — which stories were attempted, their outcomes, time spent\n2. **Issues analysis** — categorize and analyze all issues from the session log\n3. **Cost analysis** — from the cost report\n4. **What went well** — stories completed, bugs fixed, process improvements\n5. **What went wrong** — failures, blockers, stuck stories, wasted iterations\n6. **Lessons learned** — patterns to repeat or avoid\n7. **Action items** — concrete next steps\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md — append with `---` separator since the file already exists.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a3aa882605817c3fe","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective written to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md`.\n\nKey findings:\n\n- **Session 50** was the 34th consecutive no-op session fixing the same Ralph stale-state corruption (stories 16-5 through 16-8 reverted to `review`).\n- **Total sprint cost: $714.12** across 5,250 API calls for 74 completed stories.\n- **~$235 (33%) is identifiable waste** from 34 repair loops, 34 retrospectives, and phantom story \"1-1-foo\" processing.\n- **Effective cost per real story: $9.65** (excluding waste).\n- **Verification phase consumed 54.2%** of total cost ($387).\n- **The P0 action item remains: kill Ralph.** The sprint has been complete since session 16. Every session after that has been pure token burn."}],"totalDurationMs":101081,"totalTokens":40081,"totalToolUseCount":10,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3021,"cache_read_input_tokens":36822,"output_tokens":237,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3021},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
